---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use & Product Disclaimer | Amrich Pharma" description="Important usage guidelines for Amrich Pharma aquaculture products. Dosage, disease claims, veterinary advice, and liability limitations.">
  <section class="hero-band-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Use &amp; Product Disclaimer</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Effective: November 1, 2024
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        By accessing or using the Amrich Pharma website, you agree to these Terms of Use and Product Disclaimer. If you do not agree, please discontinue use immediately. These terms are governed by the laws of India.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Critical Product Disclaimers</h2>

      <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">Scientific Claims &amp; Limitations</h3>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">
        Amrich Pharma products are aquaculture health solutions designed to support pond water quality, disease management, and probiotic balance. They are not substitutes for veterinary diagnosis or prescription medications. Always consult a qualified aquaculture veterinarian for disease outbreaks.
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">Dosage &amp; Application Responsibility</h3>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">
        Farmers are responsible for applying products according to the labeled instructions. Actual results may vary based on water parameters, pond conditions, species, and weather. Amrich Pharma recommends regular water testing and consultation with local field specialists.
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">Chemical Interactions</h3>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">
        Do not mix FARM 80% with iodine-based disinfectants within 48 hours of application. Always follow the recommended sequence of treatments. For compatibility questions, contact our technical support team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Amrich Pharma shall not be held liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from product use, including crop loss, water quality degradation, or disease escalation, where products have been used as directed. Our total liability is limited to the purchase value of the product in question.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Returns, Refunds &amp; Quality Assurance</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        We stand behind every product we manufacture. If you receive a defective or damaged batch, report it within 7 days of delivery. Include your batch number, purchase date, and distributor details. We will arrange testing, replacement, or refund as appropriate.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Quality complaints: <a href="mailto:quality@amrichpharma.com">quality@amrichpharma.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Technical Support &amp; Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        For technical queries, dosage clarification, or pond management advice, contact our support team. All disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of courts in Mumbai, Maharashtra.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Amrich Pharma<br />
        Plot No. 2, Sainath Nagar, Shivaji Mandpeshwar Road, Dahisar, Mumbai-400068
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding hero-band-dark" style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color: var(--on-dark);">Need Support?</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Call or WhatsApp us for product guidance and technical assistance
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: flex; gap: var(--space-base); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="tel:+919712335338" class="btn-primary">Call 97123 35338</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919712335338" class="btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
